This Mutator will 'Replace' your current Syringe with an enhanced version focusing on self-heal only to keep it balanced, featuring:

- Much faster reload animation
- Gives you a Sprint/Boost if you are below XX HP
- Global notification to all players stating who is currrently being boosted, makes it easier to tell who is in trouble
- Config:

1. Boost Power
2. Boost Duration
3. Under what HP should the boost activate
4. Boost Message

[h1][b][u]Features that might be added[/u][/b][/h1]

- Add a slight blur overlay to show that you are currently being boosted
- Change Syringe SoundEffect
- Change Syringe Texture
- Add UI Indicated for the boost

[h1][b][u]Number Of Files[/u][/b][/h1]

- 3

[h1][b][u]File Names[/u][/b][/h1]

- \System\KFEnhancedSyringe.u
- \System\KFEnhancedSyringe.ucl
- \System\KFEnhancedSyringe.ini

[h1][b][u]Sample Config[/u][/b][/h1]

[code]
[KFEnhancedSyringe.KFEnhancedSyringe]
# If Player Below XX HP
iBoostWhen=50
# Boost Speed
iBoostPower=350
# Duration till the boost ends
iBoostDuration=3
# %BD is the number/placeholder of Boost Duration
# Color tag words using the labels below e.g. %g for green, %r for red, then put %w to make next words without color
sBoostMessage=%wYou have been fucking %rboosted%w for %g%BD%w seconds! Run the %bFuck%w Away!
# You can add more colors by using the same format of the below ColorList
ColorList=(ColorName="Red",ColorTag="%r",Color=(B=0,G=0,R=200,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Orange",ColorTag="%o",Color=(B=0,G=127,R=255,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Yellow",ColorTag="%y",Color=(B=0,G=255,R=255,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Green",ColorTag="%g",Color=(B=0,G=200,R=0,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Blue",ColorTag="%b",Color=(B=200,G=100,R=0,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Teal",ColorTag="%t",Color=(B=113,G=179,R=60,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Violet",ColorTag="%v",Color=(B=139,G=0,R=255,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="White",ColorTag="%w",Color=(B=200,G=200,R=200,A=0))
# Better to keep debugging False :)
bDebug=False
[/code]

[h1][b][u]Usage[/u][/b][/h1]

1- Subscribe or download manually (recommended)
2- Launch the game and wait to see 'Completed'
3- Restart the game and you can see the mutators in your list

[h1][b][u]Class Names[/u][/b][/h1]

- Spawn Mut: KFEnhancedSyringe.KFEnhancedSyringe

